Name: Essentials by OFM ESS-6035M Heated Shiatsu Massage Bonded Leather Executive Chair
Description of a product (romantic): The Essentials Collection seating collection is where quality meets value. The ESS-6035M upgrades the executive office chair experience with the addition of a heated, Shiatsu-style rolling/kneading adjustable full-back massage system that provides the ultimate in comfort and helps soothe muscle tension and aches. The system is controlled by a remote that attaches unobtrusively to the side of the chair when not in use. The high back, seat, and integrated headrest are designed with segmented double-plush padding for luxurious support, and are upholstered in smooth SofThread leather for an upscale look and feel. The thickly padded loop arms add style and upper body support. The ESS-6035M also offers simple and intuitive controls such as gas-lift seat height adjustment, 360 degree swivel, tilt tension, and tilt lock for even more ergonomic customizability. The comfort, stylish look, and price point of this chair make it a perfect addition to the office, whether at work or at home. This chair meets or exceeds industry standards for safety and durability, and is backed by our Essentials Collection Limited Warranty.
